title: Ep - 68 - Brandi Redmond from Real Housewives of Dallas
description:
Brandi Redmond from Real Housewives of Dallas talks about life as a Dallas Cowboy Cheerleader, why her husband thought she was a spy, the impact of reality television on her marriage, and the end of season two of the show.


Retired executive Bud Siegel gives his opinion of Naked and Afraid on the Discovery Channel. 


Podcast and writer’s assistant Michael Sherman reviews Joy Anna Duggar’s wedding episode on Counting On. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
